f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec3cfefefb0ffa7a41f1a0dd48e214da25f1210","tid":424983,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T13:38:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://www.oricon.co.jp/news/2089956/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.oricon.co.jp%2Fnews%2F2089956%2F&d=bdfRKPyRx1hzTk0oy89Qxp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=8de1ccd5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.oricon.co.jp/news/2089956/</a><br />\n點解會變左個阿嬸咁既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇佢個陣我高小定初中<br />\n依家我都大學final year <br />\n試問有幾多個不老結衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得佢個樣一時時 好似睇佢個blog最近d相又ok喎"},{"pid":"a6068e8cbfea908e270d64a93a378fdd09ccfc4a","tid":424983,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T13:39:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上年做過肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c603e827c4f1f389e428c5ed7dbbf8ba2c9628","tid":424983,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T13:42:13.000Z","msg":"有冇人聽過佢d歌😊 耐到唔記得down過邊隻碟"},{"pid":"55d9f55519d117a6195533bfa83985af4c44ca0c","tid":424983,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:10:36.000Z","msg":"清純女星年年進化　瓜子臉腫麼了<br />\n<br />\n北乃綺2005年出道時，憑著清純可愛外表，迅速集結人氣，她從前年9月成為日本電視台情報節目《ZIP!》的固定班底，近日宣告下月將從節目畢業，專心演戲，但不少人「歪樓」關注她這2年爆肥情況。<br />\n<br />\n北乃從前擁有157公分、48公斤標準身材，網友拿舊照比對，笑說「現在這位到底是誰」？更猜她「胖了20公斤吧」，還有人說「該不會是變胖了，才被節目開除」。由於該節目為早上5點半現場直播，平日2點半必須要起床、3點進公司準備，網友猜北乃作息可能不太正常，才讓她變胖這麼多。"},{"pid":"a7c7ff0f60ed6501b94557d89485a6daad9681de","tid":424983,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:12:16.000Z","msg":"她6年前被拍到與男演員佐野和真街頭熱吻、去賓館開房，玉女形象崩裂，被日本網友封為「肉食女」，螢幕曝光量也減少許多，但3年前再被捕捉到佐野和真約會畫面，舊情復燃。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20160801/640_dee722f6ae29e104c68183bf7bfa6121.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20160801%2F640_dee722f6ae29e104c68183bf7bfa6121.jpg&h=5403e9e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上年真係走晒樣😑"},{"pid":"cbbb8ccb2f33f8deb0031fc6de7e8f9953e27fc6","tid":424983,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:13:46.000Z","msg":"太陽與海同life果陣有留意佢"},{"pid":"35143a301cc36c4806acbde81578bbd7eb21912b","tid":424983,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:13:38.000Z","msg":"其實佢都唔係好老 今年好似都係廿六 不過再過多幾年個樣就唔知係點"},{"pid":"cdde8fa481e03923cec4ed518a8518e3c653c563","tid":424983,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T17:35:28.000Z","msg":"我諗佢應該係其中一個長短髮都keep到好睇既女星 之前見咁多人開post討論短髮都冇佢 可能冇人記得同識佢😂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://news.walkerplus.com/article/57947/320650_615.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.walkerplus.com%2Farticle%2F57947%2F320650_615.jpg&h=2348ad08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.moviecollection.jp/interview_new/img/227/kitanokii_main.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.moviecollection.jp%2Finterview_new%2Fimg%2F227%2Fkitanokii_main.jpg&h=36ff80ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48997a8ba65441fcbd469e22e61b28069b2adcaf","tid":424983,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T18:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pics.prcm.jp/aragakiyui/1817624/jpeg/1817624.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpics.prcm.jp%2Faragakiyui%2F1817624%2Fjpeg%2F1817624.jpeg&h=e7bb5388&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ee00dbcf761121a89328f62e88f161f2cd40bae","tid":424983,"uid":141962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy